msgstr "Gwarloa"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwimli
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/04_The_Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:574
msgid ""
"Thank you for rescuing us! Now we can help you fight the evil orcs! The main "
"cage where they keep most of the mermen is in the northwest!"
msgstr ""
"Tapadh leibh airson ar teasairginn! Nise, ’s urrainn dhuinn ur cuideachadh "
"an aghaidh nan deamhan olca! Tha am prìomh-chliabh far an cùm iad a’ "
"mhòrchuid dhen t&#8209;sluagh-mhara gu iar-thuath!"

#. [unit]: id=Heldaga, type=Merman Fighter
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/04_The_Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:596
